{"tid":812970,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"德國男與阿富汗男毆鬥後心臟病亡　引發極右示威","createTime":"2018-09-10T05:23:58.000Z","updateTime":"2018-09-10T05:28:12.000Z","uid":39464,"like":7,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"0bdd323e0023a0afd70f4f4f4c617efd0d098c33","tid":812970,"uid":39464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-10T05:23:58.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://fs.mingpao.com/ins/20180910/s00005/927be5e9c689371890c3a6af5dd0df09.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ffs.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F20180910%2Fs00005%2F927be5e9c689371890c3a6af5dd0df09.jpg&h=a6ed4f87&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n德國城市克滕（K&ouml;then）早前一名男子與阿富汗裔男毆鬥，男子其後心臟病發不治，事件觸發極右分子及反法西斯組織上街遊行。是次為德國一個月内發生第二次類似事件觸發右組織示威，令外界關注德國難民問題引發的爭議。<br />\n<br />\n據報22歲死者為德國裔男子馬克斯(Markus B)，他與兄弟早前介入一名孕婦與三名阿富汗裔男的爭執，繼而與阿富汗男毆鬥，過程中德國男跌倒並撞傷頭部。解剖報告指馬克斯死於心臟問題，確切死因仍在調查中。警方其後以涉嫌謀殺拘留兩名阿富汗18歲及20歲男子。<br />\n<br />\n當地極右分子上周日(9日)舉行集會悼念死者，與左翼組織爆發衝突，警方介入平息衝突，克滕市長呼籲市民留在家中，又表示不希望示威發展為兩星期前開姆尼茨（Chemnitz）的排外示威。<br />\n<br />\n上月中，德國東部城市開姆尼茨一名男子被兩名外國人刺死，引發極右組織排外示威，其後多人被捕。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://m.mingpao.com/ins/instantnews/web_tc/article/20180910/s00005/1536555261104\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.mingpao.com%2Fins%2Finstantnews%2Fweb_tc%2Farticle%2F20180910%2Fs00005%2F1536555261104&d=FzJLSKu%2FbYC3KX6Cw1qdVACO%2BKh2Nr2cOOQ8tL9eopA%3D&h=6f2204a3\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.mingpao.com%2Fins%2Finstantnews%2Fweb_tc%2Farticle%2F20180910%2Fs00005%2F1536555261104&h=79ddcae6\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://m.mingpao.com/ins/instantnews/web_tc/article/20180910/s00005/1536555261104</a>"},{"pid":"586a80e63420ed400b9dce1bba8e68b80acfd443","tid":812970,"uid":20816,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-10T05:28:11.000Z","msg":"伊斯蘭邪教"},{"pid":"1cad5fe5d1742a06f7b11203fd547a090ec8ddcf","tid":812970,"uid":113178,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-10T05:28:12.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}